moves.name: Absorb
moves.battle_effect: A nutrient-draining attack. The user's HP is restored by half the damage taken by the target.
moves.secondary_effect: User recovers half the damage inflicted.

moves.name: Acid
moves.battle_effect: The foe is attacked with a spray of harsh acid. It may also lower the target's Sp. Def stat.
moves.secondary_effect: May lower opponent's SP. DEF one stage.

moves.name: Acid Armor
moves.battle_effect: The user alters its cellular structure to liquefy itself, sharply raising its Defense stat.

moves.name: Acupressure
moves.battle_effect: The user applies pressure to stress points, sharply boosting one of its stats.

moves.name: Aerial Ace
moves.battle_effect: The user confounds the foe with speed, then slashes. The attack lands without fail.

moves.name: Aeroblast
moves.battle_effect: A vortex of air is shot at the foe to inflict damage. It has a high critical-hit ratio.

moves.name: Agility
moves.battle_effect: The user relaxes and lightens its body to move faster. It sharply boosts the Speed stat.

moves.name: Air Cutter
moves.battle_effect: The user launches razorlike wind to slash the foe. It has a high critical-hit ratio.

moves.name: Air Slash
moves.battle_effect: The user attacks with a blade of air that slices even the sky. It may also make the target flinch.

moves.name: Amnesia
moves.battle_effect: The user temporarily empties its mind to forget its concerns. It sharply raises the user's Sp. Def stat.
moves.secondary_effect: Raises user's SP. DEF two stages.
